Event.info: OSINT APT 30 and the Mechanics of a Long-Running Cyber Espionage Operation by FireEye

Attribute.value: long_info: This IOC contains indicators detailed in the "APT30 and the Mechanics of a Long-Running Cyber Espionage Operation" report that can be read here: https://www.fireeye.com/blog/threat-research/2015/04/apt_30_and_the_mecha.html  This IOC contains indicators for the BACKSPACE, NETEAGLE, SHIPSHAPE, SPACESHIP, and FLASHFLOOD malware families that are attributed to APT30.
